text: Enrique Jiménez (born 12 October 1944) is a Mexican wrestler. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mexico Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Oaxaca Category:Pan American Games medalists in wrestling Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Mexico Category:Wrestlers at the 1975 Pan American Games
title: Enrique Jiménez (wrestler)
